OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEddie Redmayne says it was 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fa mistake to play trans    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frole in The Danish Girl    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Actor Eddie Redmayne has said playing a
OL,6, transgender character in 2015 film The 
OL,7, Danish Girl was "a mistake".           
OL,9,FThe British star was nominated for an  
OL,10,FOscar for his role as Lile Elbe, one of
OL,11,Fthe first people in the world to have  
OL,12,Fgender reassignment surgery.           
OL,14,FThe film was praised by some at the    
OL,15,Ftime but others felt a trans actor     
OL,16,Fshould have been cast in the role.     
OL,18,F"No, I wouldn't take it on now. I made 
OL,19,Fthat film with the best intentions, but
OL,20,FI think it was a mistake," he said.    
